v><div>"An Ohio pastor was arraigned in municipal court on Thursday after being slapped with 18 zoning law violation charges related to keeping his church open around the clock to house the homeless."

OUTRAGEOUS! What kind of church is this? There's probably not even a helipad!

https://www.christianpost.com/news/ohio-pastor-arraigned-after-being-charged-for-housing-homeless.html</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ba4fDQB</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Jbelkin]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Always Dump when you're at work.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/pWC9aej</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KDnnUWB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GrvWCnt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Surely more supervisors/managers will solve this problem.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PyQa7c1.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EVy6FYs.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/N5T2YLi.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kd0Psey.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Weeks? Try years. Not putting out any more fires unless someone I like is in danger.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dlrCzcw.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tuquSiB.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3bt025n.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>One guy bragged to me that he never used a sick day. So... Did you just magically manage to be off those exact days, or were you coming in sick..?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DB7IVMn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tFow9Ml.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Can't afford overtime? Okey-doke.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/W9gqGgU.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Take a Mental Health Day.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PfgIkB3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Our manager ran away with the approved days off, so management had no idea who had what approved. It was hilarious mayhem.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ujqiXCc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>WHY IS ONLY ONE PERSON TRAINED ON DOING THE SCHEDULES?! Every time they have to leave, we get so fucked because someone has to learn on the fly.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nuqD0BK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Are they gone? Good. So let me tell you about this one time...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wsIH44P.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lcVQDTA.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9UhbV6N.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rtcsXNn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ysRBBEB.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And if they catch me doing any of those, they get mad, saying we don't need to do that right now. Bitch, nobody else is going to.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Y1sFGYS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If your manager likes you... Something's fucky.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9rk56Se.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NsrjMoY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>A classic fix.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bpLFOPw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I prefer "Act your Wage".</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JLXobZI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>They put my number on a wipe-off board in case someone needed a shift covered, and when I tried to remove it, they wrote it back and told me it had to be up there. So I switched the 3 to an 8. Fixed.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/M9ZI1x6.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>SO MUCH. My legs want me to walk faster all the time, and it's so hard to stop myself.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xMgSk6r.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fhgXpC5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NJAQodP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Yellow one should be at least 3x thicker.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tv7sVRw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ANLCtCI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Apologies for the quality, but still true.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IQBzaR1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NXEdSea.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sC9dIkw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Please punch me, I can go home early.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oRioMe1.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Work smarter, not harder.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vxrGzrm.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Also they don't care for the truth anyway. They want your tongue in their butthole.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MoRk82C.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dvWkJ4t.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Dj0xKhj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XGUmQj4.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qSUEV0d.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/pWC9aej</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Onlyhereforthelaughs]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>She plunge</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/pcLpCic</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PASWDr5.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/pcLpCic</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Iwokeupdeadthismorning]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>stay safe, alberta and beyond</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/mmtAvZj</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4aUKuaN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/mmtAvZj</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[murderedbybooba]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>When you bring home a meme you found on Imgur</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/RcBWNKW</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https:/