I know it sounds like I'm complaining but I'll drop whatever money I have into him.

I'm sorry I didn't add his age. He's only two and he's strictly inside.

Mv edit: thank you guys for all the concern and kind words. I just wish he could tell me what is wrong. I love him dearly and just lost my orange cat George two months ago so it's all very fresh and I'm struggling.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/W7uez0h</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vudumommajuju]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Beauty from within</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/XZm0XSk</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/en8WdPE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/XZm0XSk</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LegoLove1]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>*Grimace.emoji*</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/lb23Crd</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wfc2Aep.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Tweet link : https://x.com/zpleat/status/1746292191025140102?s=20</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/lb23Crd</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Mech0T1]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Phone Clear 480/?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/a6Uf6WV</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/h7smMPx.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4mnA7Cz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qET2QMJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/T7be8tk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dov2Mxr.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/a4dFfwz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BACE4LF.jpg